QSR Automations®, a leading technology provider helping businesses worldwide maximize guest delight through comprehensive hospitality automation, announced that Buffalo Wild Wings® Grill &amp; Bar has selected its ePic® Kitchen Management Solution, including the ePic Kitchen Display Software (KDS), ePic video controller and KP-3000™ keypad, as its corporate solution for complete kitchen management, and will also make the system available to its franchisees.<br>
